  "title": "MAID AGENCY - SALES EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><p>We are an established maid agency. We supply domestic helpers from Indonesia, Myanmar , Phillipines and India.</p><p><br /></p><p><strong>SALES EXECUTIVE Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform a variety of tasks to offer exceptional service to customers.</li><li>Able to work independently and with minimum supervision</li><li>Good communication and interpersonal skill</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><p>Experience working in Maid agency or Sales industry is an advantage .</p><p>Average PC knowledge in Microsoft Words & Excel.</p><p>Good communication skills with good customer service</p><p>Friendly and willing to learn attitude!</p><p><br /></p><p>Working Location : Bukit timah shopping centre &  jurong east &Tampines</p><p>Working days : 5days work a week (4 weekday and 1 weekend)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>We offer attractive package for the right candidate</strong></p>",
